'''oil_refinery_limit''' is a variable of Openttd.cfg file:

This option determines the maximum allowed distance (in tiles) from the edge of the map for an Oil Refinery.

<pre>
[game_creation]
oil_refinery_limit = 32
</pre>

'''Valid options:''' [12 <= n <= 48]

'''Default:''' 32

